7/7 (Thu) Nursing Homes vs Home Care/ EUROPEAN TOURISM 2022 – TRENDS &amp; PROSPECTS (Q1/2022) (Host: Joyce)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session 1: Nursing Homes vs Home Care<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.seniorliving.org/compare/nursing-home-vs-home-care/">https://www.seniorliving.org/compare/nu ... home-care/</a><!-- m --><br /><br /><br />Questions:<br /><br />1.Did you do research on home care, nursing care and other senior care options so you are able to make the best decision for yourself or your parents?<br />2.What are the advantages and disadvantages of living in nursing homes?<br />3.What is a good nursing home care facility?<br />4.Are there any good nursing home care facilities in Taiwan?<br />5.If you or your parents require extensive medical care around the clock, will you still prefer to live at home?<br /><br />Session 2: EUROPEAN TOURISM 2022 – TRENDS &amp; PROSPECTS (Q1/2022)<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://etc-corporate.org/reports/european-tourism-2022-trends-prospects-q1-2022/">https://etc-corporate.org/reports/europ ... s-q1-2022/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions: <br /><br />1. Taiwan is a rare holdout in the world that remains closed to tourists and still mandates quarantine for arrivals. What’s your opinion about that?<br />2. Taiwanese insurance companies have halted sales of overseas travel insurance policies that cover against medical expenses due to sudden illness, how should you do if you plan to travel overseas?<br />3. Do you think that two new omicron variants detected in a lot of countries could spark another wave?<br />4. What should you know when you're planning your trip during COVID-19?...<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Jun 24, 2022 2:19 pm</p><hr />
